data.description: $8000 closing cost assistance! Assumable loan with a 3% interest rate! Check out this fantastic Cooper Ridge home! It's a short stroll to Cooper North Elementary and tucked away on a double cul-de-sac. Built by Dan Hines in 2010, it's loaded with awesome features. As you step inside, you'll love the wood flooring in the entryway and the spacious living area with a cozy gas starter fireplace. The kitchen is a chef's dream, with a large island, granite countertops, plenty of beautiful cabinetry, a big pantry, and a unique ceiling. The master suite is a private retreat with a spa tub, separate shower, and a roomy walk-in closet. Don't miss this gem!
